title: SC Outtakes, blooper reel #01
itunes:title: SC Outtakes, blooper reel #01
description: This is outtakes that never make it on the air. Sometimes we get the strangest calls. This is stuff that happens behind the scenes that you never get to hear. We were finishing up an interview and Will sent me a picture of No Shoes Curley. Then we decided to bring Ray on.
